JAMES
v.
RABBANI 79P19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 8, 2019 William Paul James, for James, William Paul.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 7th of March 2019 by Plaintiff for Writ of Supersedeas:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of March 2019."
